API's

Tournaments:

GetAllTournaments : http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments

GetTournament by ID:  http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments/{id}

Save Tournament details: http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments

Update Tournament :  http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments/{id}

Delete Tournament : http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments/{id}

Tournament by year: http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments/getbyyear/{id}



StallionsScoreCard:


Get by match id:   http://localhost:8080/api/stallionsScorecard/{id}

Update scorecard :  http://localhost:8080/api/stallionsScorecard/{id}

Save scorecard: http://localhost:8080/api/stallionsScorecard/save

Delete scorecard: http://localhost:8080/api/stallionsScorecard/{id}


Opponent Scorecard:

Get by match id:   http://localhost:8080/api/OpponentScorecard/{id}

Update scorecard :  http://localhost:8080/api/OpponentScorecard/{id}

Save scorecard: http://localhost:8080/api/OpponentScorecard/save

Delete scorecard: http://localhost:8080/api/OpponentScorecard/{id}



Player:

Get All players:   http://localhost:8080/api/players

Get player by id: :  http://localhost:8080/api/players/{id}

Active players: http://localhost:8080/api/players/getActiveplayers

Update player details: http://localhost:8080/api/players/{id}

Save scorecard: http://localhost:8080/api/OpponentScorecard/save

Delete scorecard: http://localhost:8080/api/players/{id}


Match:

Save match details: http://localhost:8080/api/matchDetail/save

List of all matches: http://localhost:8080/api/matchDetail

Matches by tournament: http://localhost:8080/api/matchDetail/getallmatches/{id}

Match by id: http://localhost:8080/api/matchDetail/getmatch/{id}

Update match details: Match by id: http://localhost:8080/api/matchDetail/updatematch/{id}

Delete match: http://localhost:8080/api/matchDetail/{id}


Extras:

Stallions Extras:

Save :http://localhost:8080/api/totalextra/stallionstotalextra

Retrieve by id: http://localhost:8080/api/totalextra/stallionstotalextra/{id}

update: http://localhost:8080/api/totalextra/stallionstotalextra/{id}

Delete: http://localhost:8080/api/totalextra/stallionsextras/{id}



Opponents Extras

Save : http://localhost:8080/api/totalextra/opponenttotalextra

Retrieve by id: http://localhost:8080/api/totalextra/opponenttotalextra/{id}

update: http://localhost:8080/api/totalextra/opponenttotalextra/{id}

Delete: http://localhost:8080/api/totalextra/opponentextras/{id}

